<p class="">The Bill is in general terms, and if we are going to consider what a responsible Executive might do under the Ministers (Emergency Appointments) Act, every Member of this House could be created either a Minister or a Secretary.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
