<p class="">But the Government did not welcome that suggestion.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-5ff4a9c2-4b5d-4bb6-a606-1d378063262e" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
