<p class="">What would happen if it were made a Vote of confidence, as the Vote is to-day? The House would have no alternative in war-time.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-d12d06f5-d09c-4667-a3fb-d5aa870274fb" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
